  <brief_title>A Trial to Investigate Hyperglycemic and Hypoglycemic Excursions in Subjects With Type 1 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blinded Trial to Investigate Glycemic Excursions Following an Oral Mixed Meal Challenge in Subjects With Type 1 Diabetes When Concomitantly Treated With Insulin Alone or Co-administered Insulin and Glucagon</official_title>
