  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a single center, double-blind, randomized trial in subjects with type 1 diabetes&#xD;
      mellitus applying an adaptive design approach.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Subjects were be studied on two occasions, in randomized sequence, whereby glycemic&#xD;
      excursions are assessed following an oral mixed meal challenge while treated with either&#xD;
      insulin alone or co-administered insulin and glucagon.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
